        "text_MD8WVp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Mountains are one of the most powerful symbols of the human journey—physically, mentally, and emotionally. They represent strength, perseverance, and the pursuit of greater heights. For BearWell, they embody the endless journey of mind, body and spirit and the challenges we face along the way.</p><p></p><p>The mountains on our packaging symbolize the journey of life - marked by peaks of achievement and valleys of growth. The peaks are moments of celebration, where we honor the progress we’ve made and the challenges we’ve overcome. They’re not just destinations but stepping stones for what lies ahead - a chance to reflect, regroup, and prepare for the next climb. Every peak is followed by a valley, an essential stage of transformation. They challenge us to leave behind the comfort of the known, embrace the uncertainty ahead, and build the resilience needed to rise to even greater heights. Together, the peaks and valleys remind us that the journey is endless, with every phase shaping who we become.</p>",
